  "response": "Determining the best department T-shirt design at IIT Madras is subjective and depends on individual preferences. Each department at IIT Madras often puts considerable thought and creativity into their designs, and the \"best\" design can vary based on aesthetics, symbolism, and the personal connection students have with their department.\n\nIf you are a student or an alumni, you might want to check out the designs from various departments, attend events where they showcase these shirts, or ask peers for their opinions to see which ones resonate most with you. Alternatively, you can explore social media groups or campus forums where students might post pictures of their department T-shirts to help you decide which you consider the best.\n\nRemember, the best design for you could be the one that aligns with your own tastes and the values or memories you associate with your department.",
